Description: Linux text snippet manager with system tray
 A Linux text snippet manager running as a system tray application. Snippets can be organized hierarchically in groups and inserted into the active window via the tray menu. Supports English, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Hindi, Chinese, and Russian.
